It's a funny movie with lots of gore and tits during one of the most awkward sex scene I have ever seen. All in all it reminded me of those cheap movies that came out of Italy in the 70ies and 80ies by people like Lenzi, D'Amato, Margheriti and so on. That's actually kind of a complement. The biggest problem with this flick was the script. The whole deal aboz having to find items so you fight the boss at the end was too much like a videogame. How's that for a complaint? By the way, the second movie has a better script but lacks the chesticles and blood. Oh well, maybe the doctor will get it right the third time.
